snippet.title: Dont Buzz Trailer !
snippet.description:
Highly addictive game !  Avoid the wires while dragging the ring ,play for free!
 
Download for Free :

iphone :
https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/dont-buzz/id1193067749?ls=1&mt=8

Android :
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.minicleps.dontbuzz


Drag the ring from the left side to the right side without touching the wires !

the game has 4 different mode : 

- Normal Mode : has 10 different levels .

- Winter Mode : has 10 different levels .

- Dark Mode : has 10 different levels .

- Endless Mode .


What is your best score ??
